         <div type="translation" source="#marichal1979" xml:lang="fr">
            <p> . . . ] bonjour de Geminius Crescens, un âne qui tu nous a apporté, Barlas a acheté l'âne le dix des Kalendes, au revoir, je souhaite que tu te portes bien.</p>
         </div>
         <div type="translation" source="#adams1994" xml:lang="en">
            <p><note>Lines 4-7</note>:  one donkey which you brought to us, Barlas bought the donkey.</p>
         </div>
         <div type="translation" resp="#cmr" xml:lang="en">
            <p> . . . ] greetings from Geminius Crescens. One donkey which you have brought to us, Barlas bought the donkey on the tenth 
               <supplied reason="subaudible"> day before the</supplied> kalends. Farewell. I wish that you may fare well.</p>
         </div>
